title: How to find the Serial Number on your Keurig® K-Cup® System brewer
description: The serial number on your Keurig brewer is an important identification, specific to your brewer. Be sure to document this number in your Use & Care Guide.

asset.author: Keurig Inc
asset.hookText: The serial number on your Keurig brewer is an important identification, specific to your brewer. Be sure to document this number in your Use & Care Guide.

transcripts: Now when you purchased one of your eggs in the revolutionary brewing systems it's a good idea to record your brewer serial number if you ever need assistance with your keurig brewer. You'll need to reference this number when contacting us. There was a space in the use and care guide to write down your brewer serial number. You can also register your serial number online at keurig dot com the serial number on the keurig k cup brewer is on the recessed wall behind the removeable drip tray carefully removed the drip tray as it may have fluid in it. You can view this area at eye level by either lifting the brewer or bending down. You may have to use a flashlight to eliminate the area and see the number clearly if you need further assistance finding or registering your brewer serial number please contact your ID customer service at 8/6 69012739.
